{"tid":188077,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"患上絕症，最多得番一年命，上帝。。。。多謝你！！！！！","createTime":"2017-04-05T11:57:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T04:29:12.000Z","uid":2702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a158382ecb558680ee803751480344ffbbd06f43","tid":188077,"uid":2702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T11:57:31.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;節哀。。。&rdquo;<br />\n醫生望住我，一直望住。<br />\n佢個樣好傷心。<br />\n唔係扮出黎個隻。<br />\n我睇得出佢真係好傷心。<br />\n咁又係，對住一個患上末期癌症既病人<br />\n身為一個醫生，唔通笑咩。<br />\n我烏低個身，向下望住右手拎住個張診症書。<br />\n左手掩住塊面，全身狂震，抽搐。<br />\n醫生見到我咁，嘆一口氣，搭住我左邊膊頭。<br />\n到左呢刻，我已經無辦法再忍得住。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">哈</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">哈</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">哈</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">哈</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">哈</span><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">哈</span>！！！！！&quot;</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n狂喜。"},{"pid":"ef734143408e6fbe8502db3fe1f67d57c517d143","tid":188077,"uid":23785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:01:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd3f86e99597dd16b7cd222b2c4863b06fcde5ce","tid":188077,"uid":15156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:16:04.000Z","msg":"巴打加油"},{"pid":"4ff759ecbff3e318bedd106aba13a267e19138e2","tid":188077,"uid":25758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:17:23.000Z","msg":"巴打，做多d想做既事，唔好有遺憾"},{"pid":"916ec2626644713c27176bb47f259de71f505296","tid":188077,"uid":72342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:20:20.000Z","msg":"堅架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主？"},{"pid":"351639294470e35bf0d0f7ad363bd9cc0a83ef44","tid":188077,"uid":36049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:22:12.000Z","msg":"咁快就可以脫苦海"},{"pid":"500457a8aa35b4cacd0f7b1fcb3634fba8abd22f","tid":188077,"uid":22273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:22:31.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81db0b6a8b20421b5c66cd3c5922bd22833ffaed","tid":188077,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:23:13.000Z","msg":"羨慕"},{"pid":"b90e3893d0749c4832e1ccc3d6a723f23a659c5d","tid":188077,"uid":36898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:30:54.000Z","msg":"講故台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8131d38e72c15f49acb8635f7f8b27667fb4d85d","tid":188077,"uid":2702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T13:30:52.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;先生．．．保．．保重．．．&rdquo;<br />\n醫生既表情不再悲傷，而係驚訝，什至係．．恐惧。<br />\n我諗係我第一個病人，聽到自己既死期之後<br />\n唔係發呆，唔係痛哭，亦唔係接受<br />\n<br />\n而係大笑！！！<br />\n&ldquo;哈哈哈哈！！！！！ＹＥＡＨＨＨＨＨＨＨＨＨ！！！！&rdquo;<br />\n大概．．．佢以為我傷心得濟，傻左。<br />\n&ldquo;多謝你！醫生！&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;其實．．．先生你唔洗．．．其實你都仲．．＂<br />\n&ldquo;醫生，唔好意思，我唔係得番好多時間，行先！！&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;先生！我未講．．．．．完&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n我無理到佢，亦都唔想理。<br />\n因為我真係時間無多！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nＴＯＤＡＹ　ＩＳ　ＭＹ　ＮＥＷ　ＢＩＲＴＨＤＡＹ！！！！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"d6fadd5a1aec0d32af8d8a00d56eadb345725db3","tid":188077,"uid":2702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T14:08:41.000Z","msg":"我一行出醫生間房，就見到兩母女攬埋一齊。<br />\n個女喊到收唔到聲，而個呀媽攬住個女，合埋雙眼。<br />\n我記得佢地係起我入房見醫生之前，<br />\n喊住走出黎既個兩母女。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;媽，無事傢，一定醫得返好傢．．．&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;唉，醫得返好又點．．．有撚錢咩．．．仆街，早知唔慳個少少，買返份保險啦．．．屌！&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;媽！&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;我而家剩係希望，供完你讀大學先死。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我望住呢兩母女。<br />\n<br />\n個呀媽大概２０尾３０頭左右，留及肩短髮，眼大大，鼻扁扁，胸平平，可以因為患上重病，臉色有少少蒼白，但臉上化左一層淡淡既妝，顯得白裹透粉，外表不失為一位楚楚可憐既靚女。而且佢既粗口爛舌，更有一股令男人心動&rdquo;反差萌&rdquo;！<br />\n<br />\n個女就１４，１５歲，應該仲係一個初中雞，成臉都係口水鼻涕。但仔細一睇，根本就係佢呀媽既縮細版！相信大個左之後，唔會輸蝕過呀媽！"},{"pid":"73d6e623367cfc6fb137f7897d4998fa0d4ec6ac","tid":188077,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T04:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}